{"tid":1960420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"WHO在報告中再次大讚中國進入緩疫期 「經驗」助多國","createTime":"2020-04-06T07:03:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T07:38:58.000Z","uid":89543,"like":2,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"49c15cca2971581c90fc71177f069c78673250e2","tid":1960420,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T07:03:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dtPgjgS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdtPgjgS.png&h=a7e5ffa0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2020-04-06 12:49:45<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕武漢肺炎疫情全球爆發，世界衛生組織（WHO）又在5日新發布的疫情報告中「大讚」中國，稱中國經過2個月的奮戰，疫情已由「遏制階段」（containment phase）進入到「緩疫階段」（mitigation stage），特別提到「中國經驗正在幫助其他國家制定更好的應對計畫」。<br />\n<br />\n根據中國官媒《人民日報》報導，世界衛生組織（WHO）在當地時間5日發布「第76期新冠肺炎疫情報告」。除報告全球重要疫情動態外，特別在導言末段提到，與世衛組織駐中國代表加利耶博士（Gauden Galea）訪談後得出結論，中國經過2個月的奮戰，疫情已經由「遏制階段」（containment phase）進入到「緩疫階段」（mitigation stage），而「中國經驗正在幫助其他國家制定更好的應對計畫」。"},{"pid":"d40a30b4888f69eef33dec86c97fa920e5a09c01","tid":1960420,"uid":60434,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T07:03:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />力架力架"},{"pid":"73e1677775763fcd00d4ea3d49c2061d8863ec3c","tid":1960420,"uid":89543,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T07:04:00.000Z","msg":"真係好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f52ba700ad61c365f6406aa83429c79f13e9b66","tid":1960420,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T07:04:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"552978424b73a02cfc2918b75f75fac3b580439f","tid":1960420,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73e1677775763fcd00d4ea3d49c2061d8863ec3c","tid":1960420,"uid":89543,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T07:04:00.000Z","msg":"真係好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmo